description:
Dr. Emily Splichal talks all about feet, from the pretty (pedicures, polish, moisturizing) to the ugly (fungus, bunions, corns), and shares lots of helpful tips. Plus: We weigh in on Glossier's latest drop (a combo eye-and-lip cream) and discuss a new FDA study detailing how common sunscreen ingredients, including oxybenzone, are absorbed into the bloodstream.
